    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read `Sprk.Bff.Api/Options/WorkspaceOptions.cs` — confirm task 012 added `SummarizePlaybookCode` correctly.</step>
    <step order="2">Add property: `public string ChatSummarizePlaybookCode { get; set; } = "summarize-document-chat";` with XML doc referencing FR-05.</step>
    <step order="3">Add property: `public string MatterPreFillPlaybookCode { get; set; } = "create-matter-prefill";` with XML doc referencing FR-02 + NFR-07.</step>
    <step order="4">Add property: `public string ProjectPreFillPlaybookCode { get; set; } = "create-project-prefill";` with XML doc referencing FR-02 + NFR-07.</step>
    <step order="5">Add property: `public string AiSummaryPlaybookCode { get; set; } = string.Empty;` with XML doc noting "value confirmed in task 018 — populated then" + reference to FR-02.</step>
    <step order="6">Update `appsettings.Development.json` `Workspace` section: add 4 matching keys with the expected values. Leave `AiSummaryPlaybookCode` empty pending task 018.</step>
    <step order="7">Extend `tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Options/WorkspaceOptionsTests.cs` (or create) asserting all 4 properties bind from config. Verify defaults applied when config key missing.</step>
    <step order="8">Run `dotnet build src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/` + `dotnet test tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/`. Pass.</step>
    <step order="9">Measure publish size; report delta.</step>
    <step order="10">Run code-review + adr-check (Step 9.5 FULL gates).</step>
    <step order="11">Update TASK-INDEX.md: task 013 → ✅. current-task.md → ready for wave 1-C (task 014).</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
